Toe Jam <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/udraconbattlehammer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dracon Battlehammer</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 218<br> <font color=#E9D756>(11/9/01 12:21:46 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://eola.cs.ucf.edu/~holsomba/alien1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EC Whores</span><hr size=1> I don't see calling someone by the opposite gender's appelations as being insulting because the opposite gender is supposedly inferior. I see it as being insulting because you are thus saying the target is lacking in the strength's that gender should be possessed of.  This works both ways and is not meant to be discriminate to either gender in particular.<br>
<br>
Example: That guy throws like a girl.<br>
<br>
The male persona is supposedly good at sports due to physiological advantages, thus saying one is non-male means one is not good at sports. I don't see this as being insulting to girls, simply that the insult is implying the guy is lacking in traits a male should possess.<br>
<br>
Other example, previoulsly stated: That girl is pretty butch.<br>
<br>
This is a case of applying male traits to be insulting to the female.  I don't see it as being insulting to males, simply that the insult is applying the opposite gender to state the female is lacking in her own feminine strengths.<br>
<br>
The concept there is an inferior gender is an outdated and people who actually still believe this are mostly small-minded.  I'm certainly not blissfully ignorant that gender based discrimation no longer exists. What I do believe is in popular culture nowadays gender based insults are meant to point to the lack of one's own strengths rather than the inferiority of the opposite gender.<br>
<br>
My examples may not be perfect btw, but I wanted to come up with something and I'm not gonna spend an hour at work writing this, heh.<br>
